      "content": "that's what i thought. it just feels too specific though. like it's not just \"adaptive,\" it feels like it's reacting to me specifically, almost like it's watching my every move to test how i react to certain environments. do you think they'd actually run tests like that on regular people just to see how the algorithms work?",
